37	Tsunami	adults	action_guide	Jiandae kabla ya tsunami — Prepare before a tsunami	Kama unaishi pwani, jifunze njia za kwenda eneo la juu (mita 30+ au km 3 ndani). — If you live on the coast, learn routes to high ground (30m+ elevation or 3km inland).\nJua ishara za onyo: tetemeko kubwa, bahari kurudi nyuma ghafla, au mlio mkubwa. — Know the warning signs: a strong quake, the sea suddenly withdrawing, or a loud roar.\nAndaa mkoba wa dharura na panga mahali pa kukutana na familia. — Prepare a go-bag and agree a family meeting point.\nShiriki mazoezi ya uhamishaji ya jamii yako. — Take part in your community's evacuation drills.	\N	\N	1	t	2026-06-15 17:31:55.906398+00	2026-06-15 17:31:55.906398+00	before	\N	\N
38	Tsunami	adults	action_guide	Wakati wa tsunami — During a tsunami	Ukihisi tetemeko kubwa ukiwa pwani, usisubiri onyo rasmi — hama mara moja. — If you feel a strong quake at the coast, do not wait for an official warning — evacuate at once.\nKimbia kwenda eneo la juu au ndani mbali na bahari. — Move to high ground or far inland, away from the sea.\nUsirudi kuchukua mali — okoa maisha kwanza. — Do not go back for belongings — save lives first.\nKama uko majini, shika kitu kinachoelea. — If you are caught in the water, grab anything that floats.\nMawimbi huja zaidi ya moja — usirudi pwani baada ya wimbi la kwanza. — Waves come in a series — do not return after the first wave.	\N	\N	2	t	2026-06-15 17:31:55.914319+00	2026-06-15 17:31:55.914319+00	during	\N	\N
39	Tsunami	adults	action_guide	Baada ya tsunami — After a tsunami	Baki eneo la juu hadi mamlaka zitangaze ni salama. — Stay on high ground until authorities declare it safe.\nEpuka maji yaliyojaa — yanaweza kuwa na uchafu, umeme na vifusi. — Avoid floodwater — it may carry sewage, electricity and debris.\nKagua majeruhi na toa huduma ya kwanza. — Check for injuries and give first aid.\nUsinywe maji ya bomba hadi yathibitishwe; chemsha maji. — Do not drink tap water until confirmed safe; boil water.\nSikiliza redio kwa taarifa rasmi. — Listen to the radio for official information.	\N	\N	3	t	2026-06-15 17:31:55.921984+00	2026-06-15 17:31:55.921984+00	after	\N	\N
